ActConstitution Act, 1867
SubjectAdministrator of the Government of Ontario
PrecisAppointment to serve as ADMINISTRATOR of the Government of ONTARIO (1) the Hon. HEATHER J. SMITH from April 2 to 4, 2017, inclusive; and (2) the Hon. PAUL S. ROULEAU from April 5 to 6, 2017, inclusive; and (3) the Hon. KAREN M. WEILER from April 7 to 9, 2017, inclusive.
